name: 罗迪尼亚法皇国弩兵-弩
Dull Blade
desc: Even if it has obvious signs of use and is badly worn, it is sharper than an ordinary soldier's sword due to careful care. However, its balance performance is poor, so the user must get the key timing and use it skillfully in battle for success.

name: 剑
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。有着牢固的剑柄，用起来趁手，但剑刃的锋锐度一般。

name: 斧
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。斧头和斧柄结合得很牢固，但整体重量限制了其威力。

name: 枪
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。枪身的长度和韧性调校适宜，但使用起来欠缺一些穿透性。

name: 杖
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。合理的杖身重量分布使其用起来很顺手，但其蕴含的魔力并不算多。

name: 弓
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。弓身各个角度设计得很合理，但弓的最大拉力有限。

name: 暗器
desc: 铁匠铺里售卖的常规武器。以暗器的角度称得上做工精致，但用料的原因导致威力有所欠缺。

name: Standard Long Sword
desc: The Union has a long history of fighting in wars, and the classical appearance of the sword features the classic style of that era.

name: Luxite Spear of the Union
desc: The cold flash of the spearhead makes one chilly. The mysterious Luxite energy stirs in the spear and the hand of the user.

塔罗boss魔法师-蓝宝石

name: 罗迪尼亚法皇国投枪兵-枪
罗迪尼亚法皇国精英长枪兵-枪
Iron Sword
desc: A common iron sword that can be found everywhere and is often the first choice for self-defense among ordinary people. It may be somewhat unbalanced in weight and not very sharp, but when swung with force against wild beasts, it can still have some deterrent effect.

name: Spear
desc: A combination of a sharpened blade and a wooden stick. This makeshift weapon may look crude, but it's actually lightweight and easy to use. In the hands of those lacking combat experience, it can be more reliable than other weapons.

name: Iron Axe
desc: A weight-imbalanced axe that can handle rough work such as felling trees and chopping firewood. In addition to defeating enemies, it can also help conquer the daily necessities.

name: Wood Bow
desc: The bow body is made of sturdy branches and cotton threads, with key parts that are easily damaged. Fortunately, the materials can be found everywhere. The shooting posture may be more important than accuracy when using this bow.

name: Apprentice Wand
desc: At first glance, it looks like a polished ordinary tree branch that responds sluggishly to Luxite Blessing and lacks precision. However, it can be an excellent tool for testing the user's talent skills. Countless priests can still recall, even after many years, the wonderful feeling of Luxite energy flowing through their hands when they first grasped this crude wand.

name: Sharpe Sword
desc: Forged by a skilled blacksmith, this iron sword is of impressive quality, elevating the wielder's intimidation and self-assurance.

name: Glittering Sword
desc: Crafted by a master blacksmith, this iron sword has a razor-sharp edge that gleams with an icy light, making it a force to be reckoned with.

name: Pointy Spear
desc: Featuring a resilient wooden pole with excellent flexibility, this weapon has been skillfully shaped for a comfortable grip. It can be used roughly without fear of splinters, and the spearhead is a genuine metal material, polished to a gleaming finish for an impressive weapon.

name: Defensive Spear
desc: The overall structure of this weapon is solid, and the spear handle has undergone hardening treatment, making it able to withstand fierce hacking and slashing attacks. For frontline spearmen, it's a rare and dependable weapon.

name: Battle Iron Axe
desc: Although the handle may seem a bit old-fashioned, the axe blade has been carefully adjusted, making it perfect for breaking through the enemies' spears and shields. This weapon has a savage appearance, yet conceals a steady and composed temperament.

name: Heavy Iron Axe
desc: An axe that is particularly favored by those confident in their strength. Wielders must possess a stronger physical fitness, but the more they swing it, the more their muscles will grow!

name: Exquisite Wood Bow
desc: Crafted from top-quality timber with superior elasticity and hardness, and combined with a bowstring made from cow tendon, this bow inspires confidence in even the most inexperienced archer. Although accuracy may be a challenge, determination can make up for it.

name: Accurate Bow
desc: The weapon reduces deviation and can be used easily even by novices, allowing them to confidently aim at their target and sometimes even surprise themselves with an unexpected success.

name: Solid Wand
desc: With a fundamental level of precision in Luxite Blessing manipulation, this weapon is a hurdle that most apprentice priests must overcome in their journey. Before relying solely on Luxite Blessing to tackle challenges, it's essential to learn how to use the sturdy wooden handle to defend oneself.

name: Gleam Short Staff
desc: An antiquated wand that can be used for writing, tinkering, or stirring crucibles. As a well-worn wand, it may have its limitations, but it remains effective and can be relied upon by the user. If it's not working properly, simply give it a tap and restore it to its former glory.

name: Precision-forged Dagger
desc: Crafted by the sandwich steel technique with the blade forged from top-quality steel exclusively reserved for the royal guard, this sword may have been expensive to procure, but its sharpness is beyond doubt.

name: Duel Dagger
desc: With its uniquely designed gauntlet and a lightweight and highly durable blade, this sword empowers the wielder to easily parry many deadly attacks.

name: Ceremonial Knife
desc: Decorated with exquisite patterns and precious gemstones, this ceremonial dagger appears to be a work of art rather than a weapon. However, in an unguarded moment, this dagger could also become a highly dangerous weapon, capable of delivering a powerful blow.

name: Guardian Spear
desc: A standard arm weapon for palace garrisons, designed for easy production and maintenance, with a considerable level of durability.

name: Sharpe Blade Spear
desc: The long spear features a sleek and streamlined design, with a spearhead that appears to be expertly crafted like a dagger. Its head is sharp and precise, making it ideal for piercing attacks, while its double-edged blade is sharp and easy to chop with. The blade moves through the air like a biting cold wind.

name: Armor-piercing Spear
desc: To penetrate through thick armors and shields, the spearhead is infused with highly durable metal, often catching overconfident armored enemies off guard.

name: Formidable Axe
desc: The axe blade has a specialized curve, delivering a deadly blow to enemies with a well-angled strike.

name: Antimagic Axe
desc: An axe engraved with runes that absorb magic, created to help infantry soldiers survive against divine spells. It has since become a symbol of fear for many rookie conjurers.

name: Balanced Heavy Axe
desc: A finely crafted hatchet with a wonderful balance that harnesses the full strength of its wielder's body, making its weight almost imperceptible. However, this feature is not so friendly once the wielder is injured.

name: Vlder Longbow
desc: This is the signature weapon for Vlder's soldiers, made from the familiar wood of their homeland. Even in mass production, it boasts a level of precision unmatched by other techniques of similar cost.

name: Steel Crossbow
desc: The crossbow fires steel-tipped bolts that can easily penetrate thick steel plates, making even elite knights equipped with shields and plate armors hesitant to charge against it.

name: Hunting Bow
desc: The compact and lightweight short bow is an essential tool for senior hunters. Even when chasing a prey through dense forests, it can quickly and accurately shoot with its meticulously adjusted draw weight, delivering just enough force to finish off the wounded prey.

name: Gazing Orb
desc: An eerie crystal ball seems to stare back with an unfathomable pupil when looked upon deeply, gradually causing the world to fade away, leaving only oneself and a profound abyss.

name: Explosive Crystal
desc: Some priests, after mastering the release of Luxite energy, attempt to push the output of the Luxite to its limit. Among them, the most skilled can maintain a critical state of the Luxite, preventing it from shattering. This expands the range of the Luxite Blessing influence.

name: Ink Totem
desc: A totem, resembling a toy, is drawn with special ink to depict the Vlder healing mark, enhancing the healing effects of Luxite Blessing.

name: Champion Sword
desc: It contains a large amount of precious metal mixed during fabrication and has a very sharp blade, shining with an exotic color. Once it is drawn out, everyone will cheer. It has been passed down to all previous champions of Elaman Wrestling Games.

name: Spear Glaive
desc: It is a one-handed sword with a wide and thick blade. As a sword, it can push or tackle enemies, and as a shield, it can resist heavy attacks. The Luccia Army often puts warriors equipped with Spear Glaives on the forward line and even develops special tactics based on this weapon.

name: Gloomy Bayonet
desc: It's a reliable tool that wins the praise of agents from different factions. It has a concealable appearance and a design guaranteeing firm piercing when attacking. When using it, one only needs to focus on the target's weakness and the timing to attack.

name: Brutal Pike
desc: It is made for killing with its violent-looking spear and blade. Whether in spike strike or large-range sweeping, its horrible power is reminiscent of the legendary tyrant.

name: Indomitable Spear
desc: It is a classic and heavy spear. No one knows who its owner was and only learns the history that, when Elaman was invaded, the man fought against the whole army on his own all day and night and finally died. Although he didn't make it in the end, his achievement is worth being respected and remembered.

name: Overlord's Lance
desc: It can easily break a metal shield with one hit. It once belonged to an overlord of Iria, acting as both his lance and truncheon. When the overlord lost it, he finally felt relieved.

name: Moon Axe
desc: The slender, solid, and sharp axe is made with rare steel. When using it, one can concentrate the power on one point and create an unexpected chance to attack. A skillful warrior can attack the target's vital part with it.

name: Rude Hammer
desc: It is made by a Luccia Luxite Priest with an exotic design. It is made of rare timber and engraved with complex original inscriptions. The wilder the user's mind is, the less effective various types of Luxite Blessing are on it.

name: Arrogant Hammer
desc: It is a hammer from a pawnshop, which is decorated with exaggerated gems and carvings and supplements each other with the user's power. Therefore, few can use it well. It once belonged to an arrogant warrior. Although her myth was ultimately shattered, she was still highly respected.

name: Pious Javelin
desc: It is a special javelin with the blessing of the Hierophant. It is said that whoever is pious enough to the Light of Sanctuary can aim at the target in mind and make the javelin hit the target. Although people have always suspected the authenticity of the myth, no one can deny its marvelous achievements.

name: Spiral Crossbow
desc: With a special design, the crossbow mechanism can shoot spiral crossbows. Its power is far beyond piercing through armors or shields, so it's a nightmare for every heavy-armed soldier.

name: Execution Bow
desc: It has a solid appearance and is cold to touch. It can end one's pain in a flash, which means the user needs to sense others' pain more sensitively. Perhaps this is why it is slightly heavier than ordinary bows.

name: Snake Wand
desc: It is a wand with a weird shape used by a legendary Elaman Luxite Priest. When casting a spell, it can cause illusion and even greater effect on the subject than he can imagine. It is said that after the mysterious Priest declared to start studying transfiguration, he disappeared and only left this ward and some clothes.

name: Anti-Luxite Crystal
desc: It is a synthetic crystal with weird nature, which explodes whenever it touches any other Luxite. Since Luxite comes from nowhere, it can also make things disappear. This idea was first brought about and practiced by a Sorceress, who then later became legendary.

name: Wood of Life
desc: It is a block of twisted wood, representing the state of self-healing after cutting off. The totem made from it can greatly increase the user's ability of healing others. After using it multiple times, the evergreen leaves on it will gradually wither and fall.

name: Iron Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒46-饰品-N-武器46_进攻类副武器
desc: A few irregular iron blocks are strung together, with some small rust marks on them. However, as a piece of jewelry, some people still appreciate this rough and unrefined style.

name: Iron Gauntlet
editor_name: AT2沙盒47-饰品-N-武器47_生存类副武器
desc: A gauntlet crafted a long time ago that can still be used today. Rather than its actual defensive capabilities, it provides a sense of security to the wearer.

name: Bronze Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒48-饰品-R-武器48_进攻类副武器 1-
desc: Crafted from bronze and shaped like a recumbent beast, it has some weight, but it is nothing to a strong and robust warrior.

name: Brass Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒49-饰品-R-武器49_进攻类副武器 2-
desc: After careful polishing and carving, the texture of brass has become increasingly simple and exquisite, with small embellishments showcasing the wearer's exceptional financial strength.

name: Wolf Fang Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒50-饰品-R-武器50_进攻类副武器 3-
desc: Hunters often have to drive away wolf packs that harry the town and make necklaces out of their harmful fangs.

name: Armored Gauntlet
editor_name: AT2沙盒51-饰品-R-武器51_生存类副武器 1-
desc: Modified from a battle-tested shield, it may have an aged appearance, but its practicality is the greatest strength.

name: Golden Ring Gauntlet
editor_name: AT2沙盒52-饰品-R-武器52_生存类副武器 2-
desc: It is made of golden stones, with interlocking rings and a shape resembling a dense mesh. It is luxurious and magnificent, but its performance is not as impressive as its appearance.

name: Scorched Sorceress's Hat
editor_name: AT2沙盒53-饰品-R-武器53_生存类副武器 3-
desc: A hat left behind by a Sorceress with burn marks from an explosion. It seems to have effectively protected its previous owner from harm during an accident and remained undamaged.

name: Bear Claw Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒54-饰品-SR-武器54_进攻类副武器 1
desc: Although it's a claw-shape necklace, it's quite imposing. Brave hunters believe that hanging it on their chests can give them the power equivalent to that of a bear, but perhaps the power is really from the courage to face difficulties directly.

name: Wind-breaking Talisman
editor_name: AT2沙盒55-饰品-SR-武器55_进攻类副武器 2
desc: It is a talisman in Vlder's legend. It is said that if one wears it, he can sense the wind drift more sensitively.

name: Super Complete Toolkit
editor_name: AT2沙盒56-饰品-SR-武器56_进攻类副武器 3
desc: It is a well-designed and diverse toolkit that is good enough for almost any situation. The only problem is that if one unpacks it, there is a great chance that he forgets how to restore it.

name: Simple Wind Wane
editor_name: AT2沙盒57-饰品-SR-武器57_进攻类副武器 4
desc: It is a simple wind wane with certain precision, which is made of feathers, iron sheets, and crabsticks. Every Vlderian scout knows how to make it. It is of great help to fight in a valley with complex wind conditions.

name: Exquisite Arm Crossbow
editor_name: AT2沙盒58-饰品-SR-武器58_进攻类副武器 5
desc: It is a crossbow that can be hidden during normal times and shoot arrows from the arm position at critical moments, with good penetration. However, the disadvantage is that the filling operation after shooting is very time-consuming, so it has a low fault tolerance rate, making it more suitable for experienced users.

name: Wild Incense
editor_name: AT2沙盒59-饰品-SR-武器59_进攻类副武器 6
desc: It is the incense made by combining trace amounts of Luxite with various herbs, which can awaken the warriors' fighting will and stimulate greater potential.

name: Rejection Mask
editor_name: AT2沙盒60-饰品-SR-武器60_生存类副武器 1
desc: A serious-looking mask that can counteract a significant portion of the effects of Luxite Blessing. It can also help experienced priests recall their master's discipline.

name: Thorn Ring
editor_name: AT2沙盒61-饰品-SR-武器61_生存类副武器 2
desc: It was originally a type of herb used for stopping bleeding, but its side effect was found to cause users to become easily irritable. After generations of selective breeding, this thorn-woven ring can amplify the effects of anger appropriately.

name: Spiky Armor
editor_name: AT2沙盒62-饰品-SR-武器62_生存类副武器 3
desc: It is a piece of armor full of spikes. Whoever wants to attack you will also need to consider whether he can bear the consequences.

name: Evergreen Pendant
editor_name: AT2沙盒63-饰品-SR-武器63_生存类副武器 4
desc: Made of a combination of semi-Luxite and semi-jade, this pendant often promotes a quick recovery from injuries and ailments.

name: Spring Wind Herbal Drink
editor_name: AT2沙盒64-饰品-SR-武器64_生存类副武器 5
desc: Made from wild-grown medicinal herbs and crystal-clear dew, this weapon can awaken the primal survival instincts of warriors and create a resonance between their lives.

name: Blessing Ampoule
editor_name: AT2沙盒65-饰品-SR-武器65_生存类副武器 6
desc: It is a glass bottle sealed by fusing, with a bright light inside shining with warm and powerful words.

name: Lion's Fang Necklace
editor_name: AT2沙盒66-饰品-SSR1-武器66_进攻类副武器 1+
desc: In Luccian culture, wearing lion's fangs signifies the ultimate mastery of combat skills.

name: Wind Control Amulet
editor_name: AT2沙盒67-饰品-SSR1-武器67_进攻类副武器 2+
desc: It is a small pocket containing a mysterious Vlder amulet, which can be hung around the neck and has a slightly fragrant scent. It is said that it was sewn by the chieftain, and the people carrying it were surprisingly skilled at aiming in battles.

name: Maverick's Cloak
editor_name: AT2沙盒68-饰品-SSR1-武器68_进攻类副武器 3+
desc: This cloak may look humble, but it can conceal one's movements or intentions from others.

name: Precise Battle Sight
editor_name: AT2沙盒69-饰品-SSR1-武器69_进攻类副武器 4+
desc: A well-thought out design created by a retired veteran, it is a complex device with a mechanism for ballistic correction of most projectiles. While it is very useful, there is a risk of it becoming a crutch for rookie soldiers.

name: Flying Blade Armguard
editor_name: AT2沙盒70-饰品-SSR1-武器70_进攻类副武器 5+
desc: A quiet and complex blade launching device capable of loading independently and chaining multiple shots together. It is easy to use, which makes it ideal for assassination missions.

name: Berserk Incense
editor_name: AT2沙盒71-饰品-SSR1-武器71_进攻类副武器 6+
desc: The incense is made from primitive materials such as trace amounts of Luxite, animal fluids, fused resin, herbs, and ash. It can induce a state of raging fury and pain tolerance, greatly enhancing combat capabilities. For some Luccians who have difficulty in transforming themselves, it can also easily trigger their transformation.

name: Beveled Armor
editor_name: AT2沙盒72-饰品-SSR1-武器72_生存类副武器 1+
desc: It is a set of recently popular avant-garde armor, mainly designed with accurately calculated bevels to bounce most flying objects off. So the person wearing this armor is usually sent for pre-war provocation.

name: Ataraxy Ring
editor_name: AT2沙盒73-饰品-SSR1-武器73_生存类副武器 2+
desc: Priests often need to be calm and focused when guiding their strength, so the ring is forged to protect them from external disturbances.

name: Crystal Burst Armor
editor_name: AT2沙盒74-饰品-SSR1-武器74_生存类副武器 3+
desc: A highly advanced suit of armor. Thanks to its Luxite-based materials, it is capable of absorbing a significant amount of force before reflecting it back at the attacker. It is even capable of shattering weapons used on it. The design is quite unique and doesn't match any of the factions in Rodinia.

name: Cooling Powder
editor_name: AT2沙盒75-饰品-SSR1-武器75_生存类副武器 4+
desc: It is a confidential formula that enables a cool sensation throughout the body. It accelerates the healing of wounds with Luxite Blessing while providing a protective layer on the skin surface to prolong its efficacy. Highly recommended for use during summer or under intense sunlight. Travelers heading to Elaman often purchase some for their journey.

name: Breeze Herb Compound Condensed Pill
editor_name: AT2沙盒76-饰品-SSR1-武器76_生存类副武器 5+
desc: Made by mixing condensed Vltar Mountain mint with the Breeze Herbal Drink recipe, providing a longer-lasting aroma and refreshing sensation while improving focus.

name: Old Scrolls of Auguste
editor_name: AT2沙盒77-饰品-SSR1-武器77_生存类副武器 6+
desc: It is a worn notebook that contains detailed records of the knight's creed, rules, various tactics and strategies, and military management methods. Among them, one article emphasizes the importance of inspiration, written by the squadron leader Auguste.

name: Sharp Claw Blade
desc: It is a short and powerful cutting tool often used by agents, with curved claws that can quickly cut the enemy's climbing ropes, helping maintain terrain advantage.

name: Unity Sword
desc: It is a reward for Irian troops who have accomplished meritorious services in battles to inspire all soldiers to remember the importance of unity and cooperation when fighting.

name: Spiky Bow
desc: It is modified based on traditional bows that have the drawback of being only suitable for long-range combat, so that the user can boldly face pressing attackers.

name: Cooperative Bow
desc: It is equipped with feathers that can sense disruptive Luxite Blessing and is usually used to work with teammates or fight alone.

name: Bowgun of the Hanged Men
editor_name: AT2沙盒82-饰品-SR-武器82_伊利亚副武器 1
desc: Its head is made by the exclusive craft of the Hanged Men. It can not only pierce through the armor but also cause special wounds to the target.

name: Standard Grain for Irian Army
editor_name: AT2沙盒83-饰品-SR-武器83_伊利亚副武器 2
desc: Although the taste is only okay, the selected ingredients are all Irian specialties, which not only have balanced nutrition and are very filling but also remind the soldiers what they are fighting for.

name: Beheading Sickle
desc: An almost circular, hooked blade designed for efficient beheading of enemies by the Hanged Men from high places, or for painfully suspending enemies in the air. It has also become a form of torture in the Papal States.

name: Iria Emblem Sword
desc: It is a regular Iria-style sword with several Irian emblem pendants hanging on its head.

name: Iria Fighting Bow
desc: Made with lightweight yet sturdy materials, it can endure a certain amount of melee damage which makes it ideal for special operatives who might need to make a hasty retreat.

name: Cursed Bow
desc: It is a special weapon with a pitch-black appearance and an ominous aura. Although its production process is simple, it is made from very special material, and no one knows where it came from.

name: Lethal Flying Needle
editor_name: AT2沙盒88-饰品-SSR1-武器88_伊利亚副武器 1+
desc: The ointment applied on the tip of the needle seems to be mixed with strong acid and some kind of mushroom juice, which is generally not circulating on the market. It is said that one has to buy it deep in the forest of Iria.

name: Advanced Grain for Irian Army
editor_name: AT2沙盒89-饰品-SSR1-武器89_伊利亚副武器 2+
desc: It is fancier than the standard grain because it contains candy bars, dried meat, juice, and other foods that make people happy and energetic. Ordinary soldiers seldom taste it, perhaps because troops that were allocated with the standard grain have rarely returned.

name: Dim Tear
desc: It is a lackluster tear-shaped Luxite that can draw strength from grief. Sometimes it can cause some impossible hallucinations to the user.

name: Star of Console
desc: It is a small and thin piece of octagonal star Luxite. The Light of Sanctuary requires the radiant priests stationed not only to timely heal people's physical pain but also to provide spiritual comfort to them.

name: Stretchable Spear
desc: There is a mechanism at the handle that can adjust the length of the spear. It can be used for both attack and defense and only play its biggest role under unexpected situations.

name: Bitterness Lance
desc: Its tip and blade are sharp, making it sound harsh when used. Its handle is stained with black blood, and it is a weapon belonging to the avenger and the rebel.

name: Radiant Cleansing Water
editor_name: AT2沙盒94-饰品-SR-武器94_教皇国副武器 1
desc: It contains the blessing of the Judge, which is widely used in the troops of the Papal States and contributes to the overall advantage accumulated in wars.

name: Purifying Arm Guard
editor_name: AT2沙盒95-饰品-SR-武器95_教皇国副武器 2
desc: It shines with pure light that can help the wearer suppress chaotic thoughts and temporarily dispel all worries, torments, and hardships inside.

name: Bone Wand
desc: The gloomy yet stylish bone wand is the last legacy of a prominent Sanctuary Priest in the Papal States. As long as it's power is not depleted, the user's spirit will endure even after the body perishes.

name: Fragrant Case
desc: It is a portable incense case made by Vlderian Luxite Priests containing various medicine sachets. The fragrance overflows when the case is wielded, which can heal wounds and make people energetic.

name: Doom War Scythe
desc: A sickle emitting an aura of decay that can unleash its maximum power when silently approaching enemies.

name: Flail of Interrogation
desc: It is a long-handled flail with sharp spikes at the end, which can bypass the enemy's weapons and attack from behind. Although initially used as an interrogation tool, it was changed to military use because of its low utilization.

name: Judging Rebuke
editor_name: AT2沙盒100-饰品-SSR1-武器100_教皇国副武器 1+
desc: Taking the Light of Sanctuary as the truth and being free from invasion by chaos and evil, any enemy will inevitably expose their weaknesses under its strict interrogation. Pulling it out is just a ritual, and the devout heart and stern tone during recitation are the key.

name: Sanctuary Cleansing Water
editor_name: AT2沙盒101-饰品-SSR1-武器101_教皇国副武器 2+
desc: It contains the blessing of the Light of Sanctuary and has the power to turn the tide of battle. Only the important people in the turn can have it.

name: Blade of Ashes
desc: It is an intermediate product of the cutting-edge experiments by the Luxite Knights. Keeping the power of flames on the blade is not an easy task. Be careful with it, unless you don't mind turning into ashes.

name: Nobleman's Bastard Sword
desc: It seems to be the relic of a nobleman skilled in swordsmanship, with a slightly longer hilt that can be waved with one hand or both hands. It can make the user's movements more flexible and varied with smooth paces.

name: Spear of Agility
desc: It has a slender handle and a sharp spear, making it adept at piercing through the gaps in armor. No matter how thick the armor is, there will be some fatal flaws. Just wait patiently for them to appear.

name: Traveler's Stick
desc: It is a long stick made of carefully selected wood, which is lightweight, comfortable to grip, and easy for the user to make actions. In the hands of experienced travelers, it is much more threatening than it appears.

name: Sawtooth Axe
desc: Once hit by its fang-like blade, terrifying consequences will ensue.

name: Hammer of Trial
desc: When it was just cast, it was used in the trial of those who committed crimes, such as burning, killing, and plundering, thus maintaining stability and peace in its location. After a long time, the standards of good and evil seem to become neutral.

name: Patrol Bow
desc: It is used by guards patrolling the town. Its principle of use is that the first arrow shot from it is for warning, and the subsequent arrows can be shot without mercy.

name: Wing Crossbow
desc: It is a powerful crossbow used by the guards in the Mornrays Castle. It has a prominent wing decoration, and when shooting, it also sounds like the hissing of a falcon.

name: Sharp Wand
desc: With a sharp square hook-shaped head, it is an entry-level choice for Luxite Knights. It is made of metal and can smoothly accumulate Luxite energy to the tip, thus affecting targets far away. It can also be used as a short gun in emergency situations.

name: Scarlet Wand
desc: It has an eerie appearance, like the entanglement of biological meridians, and people who are affected by it will immediately feel the flow of life. Its original users were pursued indiscriminately by all factions and soon died silently in the wilderness.

name: Flickering Ring
editor_name: AT2沙盒112-饰品-SR-武器112_骑士团副武器 1
desc: It comes from a short-lived wizard among Luxite Knights. Inspired by the sudden birth of Luxite, it can make the wearer teleport in space. Most of the people who are interested in it are young priests if only the ones who are still alive are counted.

name: Honorable Armband
editor_name: AT2沙盒113-饰品-SR-武器113_骑士团副武器 2
desc: It may seem like a finely crafted sleeve decoration, but it can fully stimulate a person's potential, which is the strength of recognition.

name: Heartburn Firestone
editor_name: AT2沙盒114-饰品-SR-武器114_骑士团副武器 3
desc: It is standard optional equipment of Luxite Knights that can ignite enemies inside their armors, and anyone who sees it for the first time will be shocked by its cruelty.

name: Shield of Oath
editor_name: AT2沙盒115-饰品-SR-武器115_骑士团副武器 4
desc: It is made of extremely hard rare metal and has been passed down by multiple users for a hundred years, leaving some traces of time after experiencing hundreds of battles. Today, it is still fulfilling the oath of protection.

name: Cinderedge
desc: This sword is the pinnacle of Luxite-infused weaponry. With its blade perpetually engulfed in flames, this extraordinary and symbolic sword still awaits a knight who can fully wield it.

name: Senator Swift Sword
desc: The Council of Knights once had a knight renowned for his elegant and swift swordplay, having never been defeated in a one-on-one duel. However, his superior skills were never passed down, and only his sword was left to be preserved for future generations.

name: Skeleton Spear
desc: This legendary spear is crafted from the bones of fallen warriors, infused with sorrow, rage, and hatred, striking fear into the hearts of enemies as they are dragged into the depths.

name: Nameless Warstaff
desc: An antique designed to be deceptively solid, this weapon has its weight distributed to both ends. It can be swung with ease and still generate enough force to penetrate armor and cause internal damage to enemies. It appears to have come from the Far East.

name: Fierce Axe
desc: It will tempt the user to constantly eliminate enemies to maintain an advantage, making the mildest person become temperamentally altered. In fact, no cowardly person has ever achieved real change through it, because it only belongs to those who are already fearless.

name: Justice Voice Hammer
desc: The tuning hammer was originally used by the Union to check the tuning of the holy bells in various council halls. However, it was later discovered that this hammer had a remarkable effect when used to educate enemies, with most of them confessing their crimes after the first strike.

name: Longbow of Martyrs
desc: This longbow is a precious relic from the Second War of Light. It has been wielded by many outstanding knights in defense of their vows. Anyone who proves capable of wielding this bows will win the respect and support of the knights, and anyone struck by its arrows will find themselves marked as an enemy of the people.

name: Star Speed Crossbow
desc: This crossbow was once wielded by a former city defense general of the Union during a protracted night-time siege. Its bolts flew like shooting stars, dazzlingly fast and accurate, maintaining the defenders' high morale and turning the hopeless situation into a victorious one.

name: Focus Wand
desc: After carefully grinding several pieces of Luxite into specific arc shapes, they are combined with a wand to more precisely converge the effects of Luxite Blessing. The original crafter of this wand was also responsible for the lighting design of the Knight's Council Hall.

name: Resentment Broom
desc: It was originally a powerful healing wand specially crafted by a Sorceress as a token of love for her sweetheart. However, the recipient betrayed her, and the curse began to spread.

name: Space-time Ring
editor_name: AT2沙盒126-饰品-SSR2-武器126_骑士团副武器 1+
desc: It comes from a short-lived wizard among Luxite Knights. Inspired by the sudden birth of Luxite, it can make the wearer teleport in space. Later generations further enhanced its effect and energy endurance. To this day, nobody can resist his curiosity about it.

name: Model Armband
editor_name: AT2沙盒127-饰品-SSR2-武器127_骑士团副武器 2+
desc: It may seem like a finely crafted sleeve decoration, but it can fully stimulate the fighting will of people around, which is the strength of model.

name: Roaring Flint
editor_name: AT2沙盒128-饰品-SSR2-武器128_骑士团副武器 3+
desc: A possible weapon for the knights who make use of Luxite, containing a fragment imbued with the power of flame. After being modified, it is no longer limited to targeting single objects. Due to the extensive collateral damage, the Union finally decided to add regulations limiting its use.

name: Communication Boots
editor_name: AT2沙盒129-饰品-SSR2-武器129_骑士团副武器 4+
desc: The weapon of signalmen is their legs and shoes. The Union often launches expeditions, so it attaches great importance to its signalmen's equipment. Therefore, it specially develops such boots that can greatly reduce the burden on legs.

name: Twin Meteor Sword
editor_name: AT2沙盒130-剑-SSR3-武器130_晶石看板剑
desc: They are forged by the same meteorite iron and Luxite, perfectly mixing the hardness of iron with the performance of Luxite. The power of a single sword is already considerable, and when two swords that can sense each other are combined, the power is beyond imagination.

name: Battering Lance
editor_name: AT2沙盒131-枪-SSR3-武器131_晶石看板枪
desc: With a spear and a body made of Luxite material, it can even pierce through the thick city gate with all strength. The vast majority of armors are like pieces of paper in front of it. Few knights can withstand its counteracting force.

name: Nightmare Hammer
editor_name: AT2沙盒132-斧-SSR3-武器132_晶石看板斧
desc: Not only does it have terrifying destructive power, but as long as the user is still fighting, it can constantly restore his energy and keep him fighting endlessly. The experience of fighting against it will become a nightmare for the rest of life.

name: Star-hunting Bow
editor_name: AT2沙盒133-弓-SSR3-武器133_晶石看板弓
desc: It is a perfect weapon for sniping long-range targets. The user needs armor to protect themselves, as the impact of the arrow at the moment of departure can even affect nearby allies.

name: Semi-permanent Luxite Mechanism
editor_name: AT2沙盒134-杖-SSR3-武器134_晶石看板杖
desc: It is the best masterpiece made by Luxite Priests, which is a device containing enormous Luxite energy and is capable of partially recovering the energy released by it. Using it repeatedly in this way, fighting is as easy as breathing.

name: Radiant Bell
editor_name: AT2沙盒135-饰品-SSR3-武器135_晶石看板副武器1
desc: By directionally transmitting vibrations through Luxite, it can repel all evil forces. As they are few, every knight can only carry one Radiant Bell.

name: Plume of Light
editor_name: AT2沙盒136-饰品-SSR3-武器136_晶石看板副武器2
desc: The most outstanding Luxite Priest possesses the ability to condense the Light of Sanctuary. The back of the sculpture in the Knight's Council Hall is surrounded by solid Luxite of the Light of Sanctuary, known as the Plume of Light. It is fragile in form and very difficult to carry.

name: Dragon Aura Box
editor_name: AT2沙盒137-饰品-SSR3-武器137_晶石看板副武器3
desc: It is a special device to protect the firestone with Luxite purity exceeding the critical point and extremely unstable properties. Once the carrier decides to use it, he needs to completely close his heart and be prepared to face any cruel consequences.
